body:
This is repeated 3 times: for `noban`, `noban,download` and `download,noban`. Could avoid the repetitions with something like:

```cpp
NetWhitebindPermissions noban;
NetWhitebindPermissions noban_download;
NetWhitebindPermissions download_noban;

TryParse("noban@...", noban);
...all 6 checks...

TryParse("noban,download@...", noban_download);
BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(noban_download, noban); // just this instead of the 6 repeated checks

TryParse("download,noban@...", download_noban);
BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(download_noban, noban); // just this instead of the 6 repeated checks
```

