In addition to bugs, maintenance/code review is easier if braces are always present. Consider this:

```diff
 if ((some long expression && what is this == 123) || oh no) {
     statement 1;
+    statement 2;
 }
```

vs

```diff
- if ((some long expression && what is this == 123) || oh no)
+ if ((some long expression && what is this == 123) || oh no) {
     statement 1;
+    statement 2;
+ }
```
